		<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">﻿</span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black,avant garde; color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong>中央民族乐团新年音乐会</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial black,avant garde; color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong> （</strong><strong>靖江站）</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><strong>         时间：2012年12月27日                             地点：江苏省靖江高级中学礼堂               <br />指挥：阎伯政（国家一级指挥）             主持：王军 （国家一级演员）</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><strong>                       </strong></span></p>
 
<p> </p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一、</span>合奏《茉莉花》                                                                            江苏民歌  刘文金改编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、二胡、大提琴与乐队《菊花台》                                                周杰伦曲  陈燮阳编曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                 二胡演奏：段超（金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        大提琴演奏：王崇武（多项国际比赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、女声独唱《月亮代表我的心》                                      孙仪词  翁清溪曲  胡廷江改编</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《我是中国人》                                                                     石飞词 <span style="background-color: #ffffff;">谷</span>建芬曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        演唱：王紫菲（中华社会救助基金会形象大使）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、男声独唱《山丹丹开花红艳艳》                                                                      陕北民歌     </span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                  演唱：陈建强（星光大道无冕之王）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、琵琶独奏《琵琶语》                                                                         林海曲 吴玉霞编曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                              琵琶演奏：吴玉霞</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、合奏《渔舟凯歌》                                                                                          刘文金编配</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、女声表演唱《这山唱那山》                                                      根据苗族侗族音乐整编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">      <br /></span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、合唱《遥山夜歌》                                                  根据民族管弦乐《瑶族舞曲》改编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                                     郭兆甄词  刘铁山 茅源曲  穆祥来配器</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                               演唱：靖江市职工艺术合唱团</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> <br /></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />      <br />                     <br />                                —<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——</span></span></span>——        中场休息       —<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——<span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">——</span></span></span>——<br /><br /><br /></span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九</span>、男声四重唱《香巴拉并不遥远》                                                         黄志龙词 边洛曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《回娘家》                                                                 河北民歌 李文平编配</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            演唱：赵健、刘松焘、肖笑、张向华</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十</span>、京胡与乐队《夜深沉》                                                                    京剧曲牌  吴华改编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                             京胡演奏：李福华（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                             京二胡演奏：刘湘（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                 司鼓：李文博</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、长调、呼麦、马头琴与乐队《万马奔腾》                        齐·宝力高曲 赵东升编曲</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          长调演唱：阿木古楞</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  呼麦演唱、马头琴演奏： 吉日嘎拉、呼和兴安</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="1"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十二、合奏《光明行》                                                                         刘天华曲 彭修文改编</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                    《丰收的喜悦》                                                                    刘明源曲  刘湘改编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十三、合唱《北京市声》                                       根据老北京市声  亚雄改词 伯政编合唱</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                    《春节序曲》                                                                李焕之曲  孟卫东编合唱</span></p>
